#X text 69 17 Example setup for control unit patch.;
#X text 20 135 First value in list indicates if respective section is active. Use to activate e.g. a specific configuration of the track section.;
#X text 20 185 Second value in list indicates if section just started. Use e.g. for restart patterns or playback "starting" samples., f 60;
#X text 20 223 Third value in list indicates countdown to next section (T-4 bars). Use e.g. for longer transition samples or other events.;
#X text 20 273 Fourth value in list indicates countdown to next section (T-1 bar). Use e.g. for short transition samples.;
